                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Can be stacked with Melee Prowess , Volcanic Edge , Voltaic Strike , Virulent Scourge , and Drifting Contact for a 370% increase in Status Chance. On weapons with at least 22% base Status Chance, this allows them to achieve a total Status Chance value of 100%, allowing every strike to deal Status Effect procs."
